issue.title: Error "There are no logs to download" for first Download (Download generated files)

content.raw: BTW Sophisticated Engineering - was the run already “Terminated” - otherwise the options to download are available but no logs … which is probably expected? Note, that now the simulation is intentionally slowed down, so it takes much longer then it used to be …
